## GPU Capabilities
- Local LLM inference: up to 70B Q4 (~20 tok/s), 32B Q6 full speed, 8B at 145 tok/s
- LoRA fine-tuning: up to ~20B parameters
- Image gen: FLUX.1 in ~5s (BF16), ~1.5s in FP4 via Nunchaku/SVDQuant
