## Ollama (Running)
- CRITICAL: Set OLLAMA_NUM_CTX=4096 — default 128K context silently eats 65 GB VRAM
- Use Q4_K_M quantization for concurrent model loading
- Recommended concurrent: 14B LLM (11 GB) + FLUX (8-12 GB) + TTS (1 GB) = ~22 GB

## When This Matters
- When suggesting ML models, check they fit in 32 GB VRAM
- When recommending tools, prefer GPU-accelerated options
- CUDA Toolkit isn't installed yet — note this if training/compiling CUDA extensions is needed
- Docker isn't installed — suggest pip/npm alternatives or note when Docker is required
- For image gen, suggest FP4/Nunchaku when speed matters (Blackwell-only feature)

